Package: oar-admin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, oar-user, ${perl:Depends}, ruby, libdbd-mysql-ruby|libdbd-pg-ruby, libyaml-perl
Suggests: oar-doc, oar-server
Description: OAR batch scheduler administration tools package
 OAR is a versatile resource and task manager (also called a batch scheduler)
 for clusters and other computing infrastructures
 .
 This package installs some useful tools to help the administrator
 of a oar server (resources manipulation, admission rules edition, ...)

Package: oar-api
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, apache2 | httpd-cgi, perl-modules, libjson-perl, libwww-perl, libcgi-fast-perl, oar-common (>= 2.4.0), oar-user (>= 2.4.0)
Suggests: oar-doc, oar-server
Recommends: libxml-simple-perl, libyaml-perl
Description: OAR RESTful API
 OAR is a versatile resource and task manager (also called a batch scheduler)
 for clusters and other computing infrastructures
 .
 This package installs a RESTful API for oar users. 
 It works as a cgi into Apache.

